  "prompt": "How can I book train tickets?",
  "response": "There are several ways to book train tickets:\n\n1. Online methods:\n- Official railway websites\n- Third-party travel booking websites\n- Mobile apps of train companies\n- Online travel agencies\n\n2. At train stations:\n- Ticket counters\n- Self-service ticket machines\n\n3. Phone booking:\n- Call train company reservation hotlines\n- Call travel agency reservation centers\n\n4. Travel agencies:\n- Local or online travel agencies can help book tickets\n\nThe best method depends on your location, train company, and personal preference. Some tips:\n- Book in advance for better prices\n- Have identification ready\n- Check specific requirements for your train system\n- Compare prices across different booking platforms\n\nWould you like more specific advice about train ticket booking in a particular country or region?",
